      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到您提到了审核和投票，那提案最初是从什么状态开始的？是否需要标注触发创建的事件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "DRAFT",
        "ProposalCreated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，起始点是DRAFT状态，由ProposalCreated事件触发，对应DDD EVT 30。在DRAFT阶段需要完成提案撰写和基本的schema与策略校验。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "DRAFT",
        "ProposalCreated",
        "DDD EVT 30",
        "Authoring"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
